 filteringBySearch :(array, search)=>{
	 
	
    const result = array.filter(e => {
    const name = e.name.toLowerCase();
    const searchElem = search.toLowerCase();
    
    return name.includes(searchElem)
    });
console.log(result)
  return storeValue('array', result, false)
},

filteringByCategory: (array, category) => {
  let result = [];
  if (category === "All") {
    result = array;
  } else {
    result = array.filter((e) => e.category.includes(category) ? true : false);
  }
  return storeValue("array", result, false);
}
}
